_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">Click here<\/a> to shop for great indoor succulents from one of our favorite vendors.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-3\"><p>In general, succulents that have bright colors (such as reds, purples and oranges) don't do well indoors. They require some direct sun and more light than is generally available indoors.<\/p>\n<p>A great place to start is with succulents that are naturally green. A few great examples include <a href=\"http:\/\/www.awin1.com\/cread.php?awinaffid=233213&awinmid=6220&clickref=indoorcare_haworthias&p=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.etsy.com%2Fsearch%2Fhome-and-living%2Foutdoor-and-garden%3Fq%3Dhaworthia%2Bsucculent%26explicit%3D1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">Haworthia<\/a> and <a href=\"http:\/\/www.awin1.com\/cread.php?awinaffid=233213&awinmid=6220&clickref=indoorcare_gasterias&p=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.etsy.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Dgasteria%2520succulent\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">Gasteria<\/a> varieties like the ones pictured below.<\/p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_15517\" style=\"width: 745px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15517\" class=\"wp-image-15517 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/12\/Haworthia-fasciata-aka-Zebra-Plant-One-of-several-ideal-indoor-succulents.jpg\" alt=\"Haworthia fasciata aka Zebra Plant - One of several ideal indoor succulents\" width=\"735\" height=\"1103\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/12\/Haworthia-fasciata-aka-Zebra-Plant-One-of-several-ideal-indoor-succulents-53x80.jpg 53w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/12\/Haworthia-fasciata-aka-Zebra-Plant-One-of-several-ideal-indoor-succulents-200x300.jpg 200w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/12\/Haworthia-fasciata-aka-Zebra-Plant-One-of-several-ideal-indoor-succulents-250x375.jpg 250w, https:\/\/www.suc